{"word":"G611 - ἀποκρίνομαι - apokrínomai - ap-ok-ree'-nom-ahee - Answer","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποκρίνομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apokrínomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ok-ree'-nom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Answer</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரதியுத்தரம் பேசு, சொல்லு, பேசத்துவங்கு (நோக்கி)"},{"paragraph":"to give an answer to a question proposed, to answer"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <b>&#x03BA;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> <b>krino</b>; to <i>conclude for oneself</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>respond</i>; by Hebraism (compare [<a href=\"#/H6030 - עָנָה - ʻânâh - aw-naw'/6030\">H6030</a>]) to <i>begin to speak</i> (where an address is expected): - answer.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1252/1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253/1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469/1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178/178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631/2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632/2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633/2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917/2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919/2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920/2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922/2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923/2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924/2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350/350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351/351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470/470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610/610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611/611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612/612\">G612</a>, <a 